I have considered quitting some of the bands but I also enjoy the friendships I find with my fellow musicians. It's very complicated. I also I don't want to hurt anyone's feelings, however I am so impassioned towards my creativity I feel I owe it to myself to divert my resources towards it. I also don't want to leave the bands in an incomplete state. I wish I could do it all. I find that I feel fear somehow, regarding the actions I feel I should take.
